-- Anglo American Said to Sell 750 Million Euros of 10-Year Bonds
-- B y   H a n n a h   B e n j a m i n
-- 2012-03-20T11:04:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-20/anglo-american-said-to-sell-750-million-euros-of-10-year-bonds.html
Anglo American Plc (AAL)  plans to sell
750 million euros of 10-year bonds, according to a banker
involved in the deal.  The notes will be priced to yield 112 basis points to 118
basis points more than the benchmark mid-swap rate.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Hannah Benjamin in London at 
 hbenjamin1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
